---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Buzz Co Curbing | Our Story & Philosophy"
  description="Buzz Co Curbing — owned and operated by first responders. Serving Utah homeowners with decorative concrete curbing, same-week scheduling, and 4.9-star reviews."
>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-32 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <p class="font-data text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-warm-muted mb-4">OUR STORY</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-section-heading font-bold text-dark mb-12">About Buzz Co Curbing</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Buzz Co Curbing was originally founded by Buzz Betz in Cache Valley, Utah. In 2021, the business changed hands and is now owned and operated by first responders who brought the same work ethic they rely on every day — show up on time, do the job right, and leave things better than you found them.
        </p>

        <p class="font-body text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Under new ownership, Buzz Co has grown from a single Cache Valley operation into a franchise serving homeowners across three territories in Utah. The foundation hasn't changed: honest pricing, quality work, and a process that respects your time. What's new is the reach — more crews, more cities, and the same standard of service delivered closer to home no matter where you are along the Wasatch Front.
        </p>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8 md:p-12 my-12">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-6">Owned and operated by first responders.</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-dark/80 leading-relaxed">
            The people behind Buzz Co are the same people who respond when you call 911. That background shapes everything about how we run this business — accountability, reliability, and a commitment to doing things the right way the first time. No shortcuts, no excuses.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-dark mt-16 mb-6">Three Territories, One Standard</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Today Buzz Co operates across three territories: Cache Valley (Logan and surrounding cities), the Northern Wasatch Front (Ogden through Salt Lake City), and Utah Valley (Sandy through Provo). Each territory has its own operator, its own crew, and its own phone number — but the same process, the same quality, and the same promise: fast quote, same-week install.
        </p>

        <p class="font-body text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          That growth came from word of mouth. Cache Valley homeowners told their friends. Friends told neighbors. The reputation spread: fair pricing, clean work, and a crew that actually showed up when they said they would. In 2025, we franchised — expanding beyond Cache Valley and bringing on operators who share the same standards without sacrificing the personal service that built the reputation in the first place.
        </p>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8 md:p-12 my-12">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-6">What Makes Us Different</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4 font-body text-dark/80">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="font-data text-accent font-bold shrink-0">01</span>
              <span><strong class="text-dark">First responder owned.</strong> Accountability and reliability aren't just words on a website — they're how we operate every day, on every job.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="font-data text-accent font-bold shrink-0">02</span>
              <span><strong class="text-dark">Same-week installation.</strong> Most jobs are scheduled and installed within days of your quote. No weeks of waiting.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="font-data text-accent font-bold shrink-0">03</span>
              <span><strong class="text-dark">14 colors, 10 stamp patterns.</strong> Full customization without the premium price. We match your home, your stone, your landscape.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="font-data text-accent font-bold shrink-0">04</span>
              <span><strong class="text-dark">Design on install day.</strong> We walk the yard with you before any work begins. You choose the layout, colors, and patterns — no guessing from a phone call alone.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="font-body text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Our customers have left us a 4.9-star rating on Google. Those reviews aren't from paid promotions — they're from homeowners who got a fair quote, a fast install, and curbing they're proud to show off. That's the standard we hold ourselves to, and it's the standard we'll keep.
        </p>

        <!-- Real project photo showcase -->
        <div class="mt-16 mb-4">
          <p class="font-data text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-warm-muted mb-6">REAL PROJECTS</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
            <img
              src="/images/gallery/stone-home-decorative-curbing-mulch-bed-utah.jpg"
              alt="Decorative concrete curbing bordering mulch beds at a stone exterior home in Utah"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/gallery/winding-concrete-curbing-lawn-border-utah.jpg"
              alt="Winding S-curve concrete curbing separating lawn from mulch beds with Utah lake views"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/gallery/paver-patio-curbing-backyard-aerial-utah.jpg"
              alt="Aerial view of cobblestone paver patio with concrete curbing in a Utah backyard"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-dark/40 mt-3 text-center">
            A sample of completed projects across Utah. <a href="/gallery/" class="text-accent hover:underline">See the full gallery →</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 text-center">
          <p class="font-body text-dark/60 mb-4">Ready to see what Buzz Co can do for your yard?</p>
          <a href="/logan/get-estimate/" class="btn-primary">
            <span class="btn-bg" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="btn-text">Get a Free Estimate</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
